hopobject.body: History viagra .de The report's authors believe that countries hit by the financial crisis, job losses and other economic factors experienced the most declines in their spirits. In addition, political instability also played a factor. People in Latin American and Carribean countries saw their happiness levels go up 7 percent since 2007. However, those in the Middle East and North Africa became 11.7 percent less happy in the same period.
